{"tid":1438352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日行動POST","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T19:49:51.000Z","uid":303958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c0817b81d2258ce1f64f0b46e13bb2aa00f804e","tid":1438352,"uid":303958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:50:53.000Z","msg":"星期日有三個任務<br />\n主線任務<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong>萬人接機和你飛(持續進行中)<br />\n深水埗遊行</strong></strong></span></span><br />\n呢兩個任務可以自行加入<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得港島東遊行可以算係<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">觸發任務</span></span><br />\n我覺得需要達成條件先好開<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1福建幫打人<br />\n2冇警察執法<br />\n3我地夠手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n福建幫打人先 又冇人保護市民 <br />\n我地先去幫手 <br />\n一黎我地師出有名<br />\n二黎第二日記者仲有位入警察 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n福建幫唔出黎既未比佢地交下酒店錢囉  我地仲可以笑下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n主線完結後歡迎大家自行開副本任務<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，<br />\n時代革命。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d76878358a48418c74cb086db1366ff1ffa0e9cb","tid":1438352,"uid":303958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:51:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"950b96c4db7c5d268053d573a0b8a980a86356f9","tid":1438352,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:51:53.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccabc57c237a1a58f834b33077c78384936488a0","tid":1438352,"uid":99180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:52:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cfb911ae04943286fd005c1bca296498e0296b2","tid":1438352,"uid":66023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"【811港島東大遊行】 10號下晝4點半將進行上訴聆訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438318/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438318/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【811港島東大遊行】當日維園會照有集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438329/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438329/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrmcoLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrmcoLA.jpg&h=b4db3112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港島東集會<br />\n日期：2019年8月11日(星期日)<br />\n時間：下午1時正<br />\n地點：維多利亞公園4至6號足球場<br />\n<br />\n集會詳情有待通知<br />\n<br />\n集會以和平理性方式進行，要求政府正面回應五大訴求，唯警方選擇以種種理由拒絕遊行申請，無疑令人有感政府嘗試打壓市民的遊行權利和自由，因此我們呼籲市民更加要站出來，繼續遍地開花，堅守五大訴求。"},{"pid":"dd79e3fd73554c932c42599e8d814e612624115f","tid":1438352,"uid":303958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa51e11f5e5a68149517ca67ab244d1548356e24","tid":1438352,"uid":303958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fb68deddea36862b22620afc9bd7d723264dcf","tid":1438352,"uid":53366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:56:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e62d9c6cf7402e0c8cbf1a2d8669854c6ad3867","tid":1438352,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:49:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n香港人重點日程：<br />\n8月9-11日：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)<br />\n8月10日：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n8月10日：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n8月10日：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）<br />\n8月11日：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n8月11日：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFF4YRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFF4YRE.jpg&h=539785ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9Lc7Li.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9Lc7Li.jpg&h=8d1626e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFLHLw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFLHLw8.jpg&h=d8fae00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYaMsLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYaMsLz.jpg&h=b4f4136d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH1PqYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH1PqYA.jpg&h=5a975883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQEdSDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQEdSDA.jpg&h=da0e19d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/276scxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F276scxO.jpg&h=78ce765f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Af95J0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAf95J0h.jpg&h=5304a0a2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}